                      "name": "foundationsUsage",
                      "fill": "#7B6F64",
                      "content": "Foundation\nBackground: app background and section shells.\nSurface: white cards, inputs and panels.\nInk: body text, borders, icons and shadows.\nPrimary: main CTA and active controls.\nSupport: secondary emphasis and info accents.\nBrand Ink: logo and branded moments.",
                      "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "i9Y2p",
                      "name": "semanticUsage",
                      "fill": "#7B6F64",
                      "content": "Semantic\nError: failures and invalid states.\nWarning: caution before something becomes a problem.\nAlert: attention items that are not failures.\nSuccess: confirmation, completion and safe states.",
                      "fontFamily": "Funnel Sans",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
